<h1>🌐 Global Supply Chain Risk Intelligence Platform</h1>
<p><strong>Platform Monitoring Risiko Rantai Pasok Global</strong> — Sistem berbasis web untuk mengagregasi data dari berbagai API eksternal, menghitung skor risiko multi-dimensi per negara, dan menampilkan visualisasi geospasial.</p>
<hr>
<h2>Daftar Isi</h2>
<ol>
<li><a href="#1-arsitektur-sistem">Arsitektur Sistem</a></li>
<li><a href="#2-menu--fungsinya">Menu &amp; Fungsinya</a></li>
<li><a href="#3-halaman-dashboard-utama">Halaman Dashboard Utama</a></li>
<li><a href="#4-halaman-pendukung">Halaman Pendukung</a></li>
<li><a href="#5-risk-scoring-engine">Risk Scoring Engine</a></li>
<li><a href="#6-database">Database</a></li>
<li><a href="#7-api-endpoints">API Endpoints</a></li>
<li><a href="#8-external-apis">External APIs</a></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2>1. Arsitektur Sistem</h2>
<pre><code class="language-mermaid">graph TB
    User[User Browser] --&gt; Laravel[Laravel 12 Backend]
    Laravel --&gt; MySQL[(MySQL Database)]
    Laravel --&gt; Cache[(File Cache)]
    
    subgraph &quot;Services Layer&quot;
        Weather[OpenMeteoService]
        WorldBank[WorldBankService]
        GNews[GNewsService]
        Sentiment[SentimentService]
        Risk[RiskService]
        Currency[ExchangeRateService]
        Port[WorldPortIndexService]
    end
    
    Laravel --&gt; Weather
    Laravel --&gt; WorldBank
    Laravel --&gt; GNews
    Laravel --&gt; Sentiment
    Laravel --&gt; Risk
    Laravel --&gt; Currency
    Laravel --&gt; Port
    
    Weather --&gt; API_OpenMeteo[Open-Meteo API]
    WorldBank --&gt; API_WorldBank[World Bank API]
    GNews --&gt; API_GNews[GNews API]
    Currency --&gt; API_Exchange[ExchangeRate API]
    
    subgraph &quot;Frontend (Vite + Bootstrap 5)&quot;
        DashboardJS[dashboard.js]
        CurrencyJS[currency.js]
        PortmapJS[portmap.js]
        VizJS[viz.js]
        WatchlistJS[watchlist.js]
        AdminJS[admin.js]
    end
    
    User --&gt; DashboardJS
    User --&gt; CurrencyJS
    User --&gt; PortmapJS
    DashboardJS --&gt;|AJAX| Laravel
    CurrencyJS --&gt;|AJAX| Laravel
    PortmapJS --&gt;|AJAX| Laravel
</code></pre>
<hr>
